This paper deals with the problem of routing an unmanned aerial vehicle, which is a topic related to robotics and optimization. Therefore, cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes an approximation algorithm and heuristics, which are related to artificial intelligence and optimization, respectively, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely sub-category. The use of heuristics also suggests that the paper may be related to algorithms and data structures, hence cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is another possible sub-category. The paper also involves optimization and decision-making, which are topics related to machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) another possible sub-category. Finally, the paper involves computational results, which may involve statistical analysis and machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another possible sub-category.
